{"id":232971018,"title":"覺得無奈","content":"昨日下班去個超市買肉買菜\n準備煮一道“蘋果西打”燉肉\nhttps://i.imgur.com/3jdP5lb.jpg\n\n然後用剩下的滷汁再做一道白菜滷\n由於遲遲等不到爸媽回來\n我只好把肉夾起切塊擺盤\n剩餘一點點滷汁勾芡淋上\nhttps://i.imgur.com/EkVN75a.jpg\n放在桌上  \n因為明日早班我只好先去睡\n早上起來一看沒了 想說應該是吃完了\n覺得非常開心\n結果剛剛得知消息 我爸把整盤丟進白菜滷裡\n我整個錯愕  雖然同樣的滷汁\n但是不一樣的菜啊啊啊\n如果我要這樣\n為何不買三層肉丟進去白菜滷就好\n生氣+無奈\n有人能懂我生氣的點嗎...","excerpt":"昨日下班去個超市買肉買菜，準備煮一道“蘋果西打”燉肉，然後用剩下的滷汁再做一道白菜滷，由於遲遲等不到爸媽回來，我只好把肉夾起切塊擺盤，剩餘一點點滷汁勾芡淋上，放在桌上，因為明日早班我只好先去睡，早上起","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":true,"pinned":false,"forumId":"d7db42a8-bedb-4ea2-96a7-c9034f4dd89a","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2020-01-28T06:50:59.121Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-28T06:50:59.121Z","commentCount":7,"likeCount":24,"tags":[],"topics":[],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":false,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"烹飪","forumAlias":"cooking","school":"萬能科技大學","replyTitle":null,"gender":"M","personaSubscriptable":null,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":24}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":false,"media":[{"url":"https://i.imgur.com/3jdP5lb.jpg"},{"url":"https://i.imgur.com/EkVN75a.jpg"}],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"adbc35cb-1621-46e8-9617-a5fae81d04c1","url":"https://i.imgur.com/3jdP5lbl.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://i.imgur.com/3jdP5lbl.jpg","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/3jdP5lbl.jpg","type":"image/thumbnail","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2020-01-28T06:50:59.121Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-28T06:50:59.121Z"},{"id":"adbc35cb-1621-46e8-9617-a5fae81d04c1","url":"https://i.imgur.com/3jdP5lb.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://imgur.com/3jdP5lb","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/3jdP5lbl.jpg","type":"image/imgur","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2020-01-28T06:50:59.121Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-28T06:50:59.121Z"},{"id":"291dfb55-efca-4779-8fdd-1d7119747634","url":"https://i.imgur.com/EkVN75a.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://imgur.com/EkVN75a